#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.assign.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.assign"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.DataFrame.assign:1 of
msgid ""
"Assign new columns to a DataFrame. Returns a new object with all original"
" columns in addition to new ones. Existing columns that are re-assigned "
"will be overwritten."
msgstr ""
"为 DataFrame 分配新列。返回一个包含所有原始列以及新列的新对象。重新分配的"
"现有列将被覆盖。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.DataFrame.assign of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.DataFrame.assign:5 of
msgid ""
"The column names are keywords. If the values are callable, they are "
"computed on the DataFrame and assigned to the new columns. The callable "
"must not change input DataFrame (though pandas doesn't check it). If the "
"values are not callable, (e.g. a Series, scalar, or array), they are "
"simply assigned."
msgstr ""
"列名是关键字。如果值是可调用的，则在 DataFrame 上计算并分配给新列。可调用"
"对象不得更改输入 DataFrame（尽管 pandas 不会检查）。如果值不可调用（例如 "
"Series、标量或数组），则直接分配。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.DataFrame.assign of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.DataFrame.assign:13 of
msgid ""
"A new DataFrame with the new columns in addition to all the existing "
"columns."
msgstr "一个包含所有现有列以及新列的新 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.DataFrame.assign of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.DataFrame.assign:18 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.core.DataFrame.assign:19 of
msgid ""
"Assigning multiple columns within the same ``assign`` is possible. Later "
"items in 'kwargs' may refer to newly created or modified columns in 'df';"
" items are computed and assigned into 'df' in order."
msgstr ""
"可以在同一个 ``assign`` 中分配多个列。'kwargs' 中后面的项可以引用 'df' 中"
"新创建或修改的列；各项按顺序计算并分配到 'df' 中。"

